RSC LaTeX template files
========================

The following files in this directory are the official Royal Society of
Chemistry article ("Paper") LaTeX template, distributed by the RSC for
authors preparing journal submissions:

    rsc.bst
    rsc.bib
    mhchem.sty
    balance.sty
    caption.sty
    caption3.sty
    fancyhdr.sty
    secsty.sty
    headers/CH.{eps,pdf}
    headers/LH.{eps,pdf}
    headers/RH.{eps,pdf}
    headers/LF.{eps,pdf}
    headers/RF.{eps,pdf}

Copyright (c) The Royal Society of Chemistry. They are vendored unchanged
into this repository so that authors can build a Digital Discovery (RSC)
style submission without having to download the template separately.

The manuscript source (`main.tex`) is original to this project.
